'''1,3-偶极环加成反应'''（1,3-dipolar cycloaddition），或被称为'''Huisgen反应'''，'''Huisgen环加成反应'''，是发生在[[1,3-偶极体|1,3-偶极体]]和[[烯烃|烯烃]]、[[炔烃|炔烃]]或其衍生物之间的一个协同[[周环反应|周环]]的[[环加成反应|环加成反应]]。烯烃类化合物在反应中称'''亲偶极体'''（dipolarophile）。德国化学家Rolf Huisgen首个应用此类反应以制取五元[[杂环化合物|杂环化合物]]。<ref>{{cite journal | title = Kinetics and Mechanism of 1,3-偶极环加成反应 | first = Rolf | last = Huisgen | journal = [[应用化学_(期刊)|应用化学]] | volume = 2 | issue = 11 | date = November 1963 | pages = 633–645 | url = http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/cgi-bin/abstract/106572717/ABSTRACT | doi = 10.1002/anie.196306331 | format = abstract | author =  | access-date = 2008-09-25 | archive-url = https://archive.today/20121211070409/http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/cgi-bin/abstract/106572717/ABSTRACT | archive-date = 2012-12-11 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = 1,3-Dipolar Cycloadditions. Past and Future | first = Rolf | last = Huisgen | journal = [[应用化学_(期刊)|应用化学]] | volume = 2 | issue = 10 | date = October 1963 | pages = 565–598 | url = http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/cgi-bin/abstract/106572678/ABSTRACT | doi = 10.1002/anie.196305651 | format = abstract |archive-url=https://archive.ph/uPQv |archive-date=2012-12-16 }}</ref>

